<style>
    body {
        font-family: "Roboto", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 300;
    }
    p {
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 0 0 10px;   
    }
    .demo-header {
        text-align: center;
        background:
            linear-gradient(
              rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), 
              rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)
            ), 
            url(<%= asset_path "indonaz-chapel.jpg" %>) no-repeat center center scroll;
        color: #fff;
        -webkit-background-size: cover;
        -moz-background-size: cover;
        background-size: cover;
        -o-background-size: cover;
        padding: 100px 0;
    }
    .demo-header p {
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 0 0 10px;  
        display: block;
        -webkit-margin-before: 1em;
        -webkit-margin-after: 1em;
        -webkit-margin-start: 0px;
        -webkit-margin-end: 0px; 
    }
    .demo-header h1 {
        font-size: 42px;
        font-family: "Raleway", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 900;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .btn-outline-light:hover, .btn-outline-light:focus {
        color: #ef4035;
        background: white;
        outline: none;
    }
    .btn.focus, .btn:focus, .btn:hover {
        color: #333;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover, a:focus {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:focus, a:hover {
        color: #23527c;
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
    a:active, a:hover {
        outline: 0;
    }
    .btn {
        border-radius: 0;
        padding: 12px 18px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .btn-outline-light {
        color: white;
        border: 1px solid white;
        background: transparent;
        -webkit-transition: all 0.5s;
        -moz-transition: all 0.5s;
        transition: all 0.5s;
    }
    .btn, .input-group-btn {
        border-radius: 0 !important;
        -webkit-transition: all 0.5s;
        -moz-transition: all 0.5s;
        transition: all 0.5s;
    }
    hr.colored {
        border-color: white;
    }
    hr {
        max-width: 200px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        border-top: 1px solid white;
        border-bottom: 1px solid white;
        height: 2px;
    }
    .preview-pane {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 100px;
        margin-top: 100px;
        padding: 15px 50px;
    }
</style>

<div class="demo-header">
    <div class="demo-header-content">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Welcome to Indonazarene!</h1>
            <hr class="colored">
            <!-- <p>All of the sample layouts are included with your download. Select an example layout below to preview!</p> -->
            <p>Indonazarene adalah gereja komunitas Indonesia di Bay Area. Kami bernaung dibawah gereja pusat Nazarene.</p>
            <ul class="list-inline cta-list">
                <li>
                    <a href="#previews" class="btn btn-outline-light page-scroll-demo">Visi Kami</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="docs/index.html" class="btn btn-outline-light page-scroll-demo">Misi Kami</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <div class="preview-pane">
            <h3>Visi Kami</h3>
            <hr class="colored">
            <p class="text-muted">
                Menjadi gereja yang <strong>menyenangkan hati Allah</strong>, tempat <strong>persekutuan keluarga Allah</strong> yang saling mengasihi,
            </p>
                    
            <p class="text-muted">
                tempat bertumbuh bersama untuk <strong>menjadi serupa dengan Kristus</strong>, 
            </p>
                    
            <p class="text-muted">
                tempat <strong>memperlengkapi pelayan-pelayan Kristus</strong>
                untuk <strong>menjalankan Amanat Agung</strong> 
            </p>
                    
            <p class="text-muted">
                dan untuk <strong>menggenapi rencana Allah</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>